archimate:Product.name: Osprey
archimate:Product.documentation: Osprey: Osprey is a software platform for the visualization of complex biological interaction networks. Osprey builds graphical representations from Gene Ontology (GO) annotated interaction data maintained by the BioGRID. at https://osprey.thebiogrid.org/ Not anymore in active development, to use embeded viewer via the BioGRID or Cytoscape Desktop
